FORM
						Yes     No

Does the abstract adequately reflect the contents? No

 I think it should be stated in the abstract that this work is done in
 the context   where the  combination   of the  individual  constraint
 evaluations  is the sum (or  more generally,  an aggregation operator
 with a partial inverse). This is indeed a very important assumption.
 
